OL,3,C400bn euros price tag for united
OL,4,CIreland 'just wrong', expert says
OL,6,FA recent report which suggested that a
OL,7,Funited Ireland would cost 400 billion
OL,8,Feuros is "widely inaccurate", a
OL,9,Fleading academic has contended.
OL,11,FLast month, a report from the
OL,12,FInstitute of International and
OL,13,FEuropean Affairs (IIEA) calculated the
OL,14,Fcost of unification at 20 billion a
OL,15,Fyear for two decades.
