OL,3,C400bn euros price tag for united
OL,4,CIreland 'just wrong', expert says
OL,6,FThe analysis took into account the
OL,7,Fcurrent level of funding Northern
OL,8,FIreland receives from the British
OL,9,FGovernment, as well as the share of UK
OL,10,Fnational debt it presumed the province
OL,11,Fwould carry into a unified state.
OL,13,FIt was authored by Prof John
OL,14,FFitzGerald, adjunct professor at
OL,15,FTrinity College Dublin, and DCU
OL,16,Feconomics professor Edgar Morgenroth.
