OL,3,C400bn euros price tag for united
OL,4,CIreland 'just wrong', expert says
OL,6,FHowever, DCU's vice president of
OL,7,Fresearch cast significant doubt on the
OL,8,Fstudy on Thursday as he calculated a
OL,9,Ftrue total of 25 billion euros spread
OL,10,Facross 10 years.
OL,12,FProf John Doyle told the Oireachtas
OL,13,FCommittee on the Good Friday Agreement
OL,14,Fthat the IIEA study "contains
OL,15,Fsignificant errors and is based on
OL,16,Fentirely unreasonable assumptions".
OL,18,FHe added: "Consequently, the figures
OL,19,Fin the report are not even a worst-
OL,20,Fcase scenario ` they are just wrong."
