OL,3,C400bn euros price tag for united
OL,4,CIreland 'just wrong', expert says
OL,6,FThe IIEA report includes an annual
OL,7,Fcost of 3.8 billion euros to bring
OL,8,Faverage pensions in NI up to average
OL,9,Frates in the Republic.
OL,11,FHowever, Prof Doyle said that it was
OL,12,F"highly unlikely" to assume the state
OL,13,Fwould cover the entire cost of the
OL,14,Fincrease and that the figure again
OL,15,Ffailed to account for tax to be paid
OL,16,Fon the pensions of those with higher
OL,17,Foutcomes.
OL,19,FHe calculated the true cost at 400
OL,20,Fmillion euros per annum.
