OL,3,C400bn euros price tag for united
OL,4,CIreland 'just wrong', expert says
OL,6,FProf Doyle, who has expertise in cross-
OL,7,Fborder studies, said the IIEA report
OL,8,F"uncritically" uses the UK
OL,9,FGovernment's figure for a subvention
OL,10,Fto Northern Ireland of #10 billion as
OL,11,Fa starting point for the fiscal
OL,12,Fbalance of a united state.
OL,14,F"It completely ignores recent research
OL,15,Fon this issue. For example, it
OL,16,Fincludes the full cost of both state
OL,17,Fdebt and pensions, currently paid by
OL,18,Fthe UK, and which are part of the UK
OL,19,Fsubvention figure.
