OL,3,C400bn euros price tag for united
OL,4,CIreland 'just wrong', expert says
OL,6,F"It is impossible in reality, that
OL,7,Fafter negotiations between the Irish
OL,8,Fand British Governments, and where the
OL,9,FBritish side abandon all
OL,10,Fresponsibility for paying pensions to
OL,11,Fthose who have paid national insurance
OL,12,For employer-based public sector
OL,13,Fpension contributions, that the Irish
OL,14,Fside would then volunteer to pay a pro-
OL,15,Frate share of UK state debt, for which
OL,16,Fthey have no legal liability.
