OL,4,CIreland 'just wrong', expert says
OL,6,F"This is not a question of the debt
OL,7,Fbeing waived, as the IIEA report
OL,8,Fsuggests. The state debt is owed by
OL,9,Fthe UK and not by Ireland or Northern
OL,10,FIreland."
OL,12,FProf Doyle said it "is not believable"
OL,13,Fthat the Government of a united
OL,14,FIreland would agree to be left with
OL,15,Fliability for both debt and pensions.
