OL,6,FAdditionally, he told committee
OL,7,Fmembers that the previous study
OL,8,Fexcluded any analysis of economic
OL,9,Fgrowth after unification and contained
OL,10,Fassumptions that other areas would not
OL,11,Fchange.
OL,13,F"This is a very unlikely outcome. Why
OL,14,Fwould Belfast perform so much worse
OL,15,Fthan Cork and Kerry with the same EU
OL,16,Faccess, policies, education and tax
OL,17,Fsystem?"
