OL,6,FProf Doyle put forward his own
OL,7,Fcalculations which would see Northern
OL,8,FIreland running a surplus after
OL,9,Fapproximately a decade.
OL,11,FHe told the committee that the opening
OL,12,Fdeficit for Northern Ireland in a
OL,13,FUnited Ireland would be 1.5 billion
OL,14,Feuros, taking account of debt,
OL,15,Fpensions, defence and tax changes.
