OL,3,C400bn euros price tag for united
OL,4,CIreland 'just wrong', expert says
OL,6,FHe also said there would be an
OL,7,Fincrease in public spending of a
OL,8,Ffurther one billion euros per annum to
OL,9,Fcover the cost of likely policy
OL,10,Fdecisions, including to state pensions
OL,11,Fand public-sector salaries.
OL,13,F"An increase in the underlying growth
OL,14,Frate in Northern Ireland, of 2% above
OL,15,Frecent long-term patterns would see
OL,16,Fthe costs of transition covered and
OL,17,Fthe fiscal deficit ended in
OL,18,Fapproximately 10 years, after which
OL,19,FNorthern Ireland would run a surplus.
