OL,6,F"In this case, the level of transition
OL,7,Fcosts can be covered by the Irish
OL,8,Fstate, through a modest increase in
OL,9,Fborrowing or taxation."
OL,11,FSeamus McGuinness, adjunct professor
OL,12,Fat TCD and research co-ordinator with
OL,13,Fthe Economic and Social Research
OL,14,FInstitute, also told the committee the
OL,15,FIIEA's 20 billion per year figure was
OL,16,Fnot "plausible".
OL,18,FProf McGuinness added: "We do not
OL,19,Fbelieve the figures in that report
OL,20,Frepresent a realistic scenario that
OL,21,Fwould feasibly occur."
